
1.
prerequisite: configure.ac 
autoconf -> configure
output is recorded in config.log - Platform, Core tests, Running config.staus, Cache variable, Output variables, confdefs.h
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
2.
prerequisite: Makefile.am
automake -> Makefile.in
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

autoheader -> config.h.in

generated files - configure, Makefile.in, Makefile - should not be modified
                - difficult to read, read configure.ac and Makefile.am instead

1 and 2 can be managed by: autoreconfig

3.
libtool - designate static/ shared lib
use *.la, *.lo file
